":32342,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T23:28:27.000Z","msg":"關助攻咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nAMCHAM <br />\n之前已經教晒你林鄭路<br />\n<br />\n講到明解決政治問題既<br />\n係特區政府度<br />\n<br />\n只有特區政府回應<br />\n先可以回復社會平靜喎<br />\n<br />\n無啦啦點會推左責任落示威者到呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E4SCkLg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE4SCkLg.png&h=e539f3c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T23:29:04.000Z","msg":"責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8420c8651fd514ca617f2c9a74dd270f3228be1","tid":1430711,"uid":61517,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"5c2dfab0225b0ba765db42682a24dc650b756079","tid":1430711,"uid":271539,"like":16,"dislike":260,"score":-244,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T21:33:50.000Z","msg":"咁即係對香港逆權人士信任度降低級別?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T23:32:04.000Z","msg":"一係唔識字<br />\n一係五毛狗"},{"pid":"da4c405dd9f01e26b9a154841666e21ce79e0854","tid":1430711,"uid":1989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T23:34:22.000Z","msg":"風向三毛收檔啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95e0f9c91ac32674cf267d87a6d1272240849bdb","tid":1430711,"uid":74824,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T23:37:05.000Z","msg":"死五毛<br />\n有機會俾我試下新功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6640f74e44b4b73d306176920d1596a8de50f202","tid":1430711,"uid":55215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T23:41:29.000Z","msg":"P牌三毛狗食屎啦又喺度分身自推"},{"pid":"6f9b9a26582c59f460485b7123496d549a2007ef","tid":1430711,"uid":281926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02b858b0702ae201587e4085838c93c41a75125d","tid":1430711,"uid":271539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T21:32:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.voacantonese.com/a/cantonese-ry-us-travel-advisory-level-two-to-hong-kong-20190807-ry/5033183.html?fbclid=IwAR2L0j8VusIXJcAPkEiXNvlnq9RbXxtZalFTOTdnh6Wg5cr5D6LXdzxZQqY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Fa%2Fcantonese-ry-us-travel-advisory-level-two-to-hong-kong-20190807-ry%2F5033183.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2L0j8VusIXJcAPkEiXNvlnq9RbXxtZalFTOTdnh6Wg5cr5D6LXdzxZQqY&d=zO4uXE7qxnklPfV4Vu9eJZMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=ec7c8303\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voacantonese.com/a/cantonese-ry-us-travel-advisory-level-two-to-hong-kong-20190807-ry/5033183.html?fbclid=IwAR2L0j8VusIXJcAPkEiXNvlnq9RbXxtZalFTOTdnh6Wg5cr5D6LXdzxZQqY</a><br />\n<br />\n華盛頓 &mdash; <br />\n美國國務院在東岸時間星期三下午在官方網站上宣布，提升對香港的旅遊警示到第二級別(Level Two)。<br />\n<br />\n據旅遊警示的內容說，由於香港出現內亂，呼籲美國公民在香港境內活動時需要更加謹慎。<br />\n<br />\n這份旅遊警示說，自從2019年6六月以來，香港各地均舉行多次大規模及較小規模的政治示威活動。雖然大多數參與者都很和平，但有部分參與者變得對抗或演變成暴力衝突。事件發生的地點除了在被香港警方允許舉行遊行或集會的社區外，抗議和對抗事件已經蔓延到多個社區。這些在很短的時間或根本沒有事先宣布的情況下發生的示威活動有可能在短期內持續進行。<br />\n<br />\n旅遊警示呼籲在香港的美國公民需要密切留意當地媒體的新聞報導，避免前往發生示威抗議的社區，如果身處示威地點附近時務必謹慎行事，並注意週圍環境與保持低調。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T23:41:37.000Z","msg":"正評俾旅遊警示，但樓主係鬼想帶風向<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住：<br />\nIf we burn, you burn with us <br />\n<br />\n來攬炒吧！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c09b2d48a59f7c5f24d1f1fd6877f4c8d435234c","tid":1430711,"uid":163493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T23:47:32.000Z","msg":"凸發 BREAKING! - 狗總爆發手足口病數警染病  - 皇天擊殺<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1430770\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1430770</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a5fa273ca3cdd87fe64a03cc427ca3f32b93af52","tid":1430711,"uid":54303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"